    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is offset by the high relevance of the validation scenario to the COU, the multi-laboratory experimental dataset, and the conservative acceptance bounds applied to the output comparison. The overall credibility of the FEA model for the stated COU is assessed as sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision. The package is accepted for submission.",
